# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_0000000> (extension value specification)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_0000000> "extension value specification"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_0000000> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001931>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_0000001> (testing recipe)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_0000001> "testing recipe"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_0000001> "")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_0000001> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0060008>)

