# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000037> (secondary creep region)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000037> "https://www.iso.org/standard/67737.html")
