AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000038> "tertiary creep region"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000038> "The final creep stage marked by accelerated creep rate leading to material failure.")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000038> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000009>)

