AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000042> "grain boundary creep mechanism"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000042> "Deformation caused by the sliding of grains past one another (often Coble creep).")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000042> <https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000303>)

