# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000052> (activation energy value specification)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000052> "activation energy value specification"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000052> "An activation energy value specification is a scalar value specification representing the calculated quantitative measurement of the thermal energy barrier (typically denoted as Qc​) required to initiate and sustain the dominant thermally activated creep deformation mechanism within the material.")
EquivalentClasses(<https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000052> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001931> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000058> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020162>)))
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000052> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001931>)

