AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000062> "A test duration value specification is a scalar value specification representing the total measured time elapsed from the initial application of the test force until the formal completion, rupture, or termination of the test.")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000062> <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000065>)

