AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_00000127> "Testing machine that permits straining of more than one test piece simultaneously.")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_00000127> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000602>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000779> (Wärmebehandlung)

EquivalentClasses(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000779> ObjectIntersectionOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000779> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000062> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000833>)))

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000302> (uncertainty datum)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000302> "uncertainty datum")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000302> "An uncertainty datum is a quantitative information entity that specifies the calculated margin of error or the estimated range of values within which the true value of a specific recorded measurement (such as temperature, applied force, or extension) is statistically expected to lie, typically calculated according to standard laboratory practices (such as ISO 204 Annex E).")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000302> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000027>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000303> (deformation mechanism specification datum)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000303> "deformation mechanism specification datum")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000303> "A deformation mechanism specification datum is an information entity that identifies and records the specific microstructural or crystallographic process—such as dislocation creep, diffusional flow, or grain boundary sliding—that is determined to be the primary physical cause of the deformation observed in the material during the test.")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000303> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0060009>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000304> (stress)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000304> "stress")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000304> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000019>)


)